Hyundai Elantra
Price -Rs. 15.88 - 20.39 Lakh
Elantra Specs, Features and Price The Hyundai Elantra has 1 Petrol Engine on offer. The Petrol engine is 1999 cc. It is available with the Manual and Automatic transmission. Depending upon the variant and fuel type the Elantra has a mileage of 14.59 to 14.62 kmpl. The Elantra is a 5 seater Sedan and has a length of 4620mm, width of 1800mm and a wheelbase of 2700mm.
